msgstr "Попробуйте сами!"

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/raster_data.rst:313
msgid "Here are some ideas for you to try with your learners:"
msgstr "Вот некоторые идеи для заданий:"

#: ../../docs/gentle_gis_introduction/raster_data.rst:315
msgid ""
"Discuss with your learners in which situations you would use raster data and"
